{"tid":447994,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[尋人] 10月25日青衣碼頭黑衫黑褲嗰位先生","createTime":"2017-10-25T22:54:10.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-26T00:29:17.000Z","uid":114539,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"72c0f272c8e3a7e63da7a8634ddfe117714aebdc","tid":447994,"uid":114539,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T22:54:10.000Z","msg":"話說 尋晚因為一啲問題而好傷心好傷心 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n坐咗喺青衣碼頭近運動場方向嘅岸邊<br />\n坐咗兩三個鐘 抱住自己咁蹲係到<br />\n<br />\n其間有個男仔一直企喺好近嘅地方 企咗一兩個鐘<br />\n雖然唔知你係等緊人定真係咁無聊企係到<br />\n但係我朋友嚟到嘅時候問我識唔識你 佢話見到你望住我 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n可能你係好奇緊個痴線婆係到做緊咩<br />\n但係如果你係因為擔心我會跳海而企係到陪我嘅話 好感激你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我feel到你會望下我做緊咩 我朋友一到你就走咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好想搵返你 如果你見到呢個post就留個言<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2e928c9f2dec92775893787a9420f55cbfbf6010","tid":447994,"uid":3818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T22:56:20.000Z","msg":"諗多左左啦你"},{"pid":"091e45d11e3483e59aba87d0c5b804b521e25f15","tid":447994,"uid":60986,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T22:56:21.000Z","msg":"係愛呀，哈利！"},{"pid":"5b5732e83ac6f7f097833065266517f564aba96e","tid":447994,"uid":2506,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T22:57:33.000Z","msg":"其實係我想跳海 但見到有人唔跳住<br />\n之後望左你好耐你都未走<br />\n仲要有個fd黎同你吹水 心知你地有排吹<br />\n所以我咪擇日再跳"},{"pid":"583e92c3f8b8faa0d479550c32e6d7b61e288210","tid":447994,"uid":114539,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T22:58:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>諗多左左啦你</blockquote><br />\n可能真係諗多<br />\n但係傷心嘅時候有人企係隔離一兩個鐘咁擋海風真係冇咁凍同sad<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e05f7be50f2bcfd72e356bcfba13cd134d3d5e3e","tid